    http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/finance/v0

    ValueWithAttributes CustomerLoyalty

      • http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/finance/v0:CustomerLoyalty

      • Description

        Program rewarding frequent use by accumulating credits for services provided by vendors.

    • Example XML

      • Indicator Summary

        Indicators 
        Name Description
        expireDateExclusiveIndicatorInd
        When true, indicates that the ExpireDate is the first day after the applicable period (e.g. when expire date is Oct 15 the last date of the period is Oct 14).
        primaryLoyaltyIndicatorInd
        When true, indicates this is the primary customer loyalty program and when false, indicates this is not the primary customer loyalty program.
